- The fix was applied to the correct target file: `gson/src/main/java/com/google/gson/internal/$Gson$Types.java`
- I verified that existing tests still pass, confirming the fix doesn't break existing functionality
- A patch file (`enlightened_fix.patch`) was generated containing only the necessary changes
- The patch does not contain any changes to `pom.xml` or `build.xml` as required

The fix addresses the type resolution issue that prevents proper deserialization of generic types with wildcards, which is the core of the Gson-18 bug.

